                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18331128-36-off211 t18331128-36-cd212"></join>, 7 napkins, value 3s.; 1 frock, value 2s.; 1 sheet, value 1s.; 1 shawl, value 6d.; 1 pillow-case, value 3d.; 1/2 a yard of muslin, value 6d.; 1 towel, value 2d.; and 1 bottle, value 2d.
